{"lc": 1, "type": "constructor", "id": ["langchain", "schema", "document", "Document"], "kwargs": {"page_content": "How to calculate accumulated GPA for BUV Own Degree students? C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh \u0110i\u1ec3m Trung b\u00ecnh t\u00edch l\u0169y GPA cho sinh vi\u00ean h\u1ec7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam BUV nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?\n\nAnswer / C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi:\n\nFor students who are studying BUV program, the assessment of students\u2019 learning outcome by academic year is performed based on the grade point average (GPA) of that academic year. / \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi sinh vi\u00ean \u0111ang theo h\u1ecdc ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc BUV, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a sinh vi\u00ean theo k\u1ef3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh (GPA) c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3.\n\nGrading Scale before 9 April 2024 / Thang t\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 09/04/2024 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc\n\nThis grading scale follows Circular 08/2021/TT-BGD\u0110T of the Ministry of Education and Training promulgating regulation on undergraduate education./Thang \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y tu\u00e2n theo Th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 08/2021/TT-BGD\u0110T c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ban h\u00e0nh quy ch\u1ebf gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc.\n\nFor this reason, all assessments are graded on the 100-scores-scale which are automatically converted into 10-scores-scale using the formula reported to Ministry of Education and Training. / V\u00ec l\u00fd do n\u00e0y, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m theo thang \u0111i\u1ec3m 100 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n sang thang \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 theo c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1o c\u00e1o B\u1ed9 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o.\n\nBelow is the conversion table / D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng quy \u0111\u1ed5i:\n\n| 100 scores scale Thang \u0111i\u1ec3m 100 | 10 scores scale Thang \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 | Letter Grade \u0110i\u1ec3m b\u1eb1ng ch\u1eef | GPA score \u0110i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh t\u00ednh theo h\u1ec7 4 | Note Ghi ch\u00fa |\n| - | - | - | - | - |\n| 70-100 | 8.5-10.00 | A | 4 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 60-69 | 7.00-8.40 | B | 3 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 50-59 | 5.50-6.90 | C | 2 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 40-49 | 4.00-5.40 | D | 1 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 0-39 | 0-3.90 | F | 0 | Fail / Tr\u01b0\u1ee3t |\n\nGrading Scale since 9 April 2024 / Thang t\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 09/04/2024 tr\u1edf \u0111i\n\nIn accordance with Circular 08/2021 of Ministry of Education and Training, to ensure fairness to all BUV students studying Vietnamese degrees in one class, all classes, all courses, and all modes of study, on 9 April 2024, the Senate of British University Vietnam has approved with immediate effect the new marking scheme where more letter grades are applied based on 100-scale marks. / Theo Th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 08/2021 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 sinh vi\u00ean BUV \u0111ang theo h\u1ecdc ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc Anh Qu\u1ed1c Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c l\u1edbp, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc, v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 9 th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m 2024, H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng khoa h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Anh Qu\u1ed1c Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1edbi, trong \u0111\u00f3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eb1ng ch\u1eef d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean thang \u0111i\u1ec3m 100 nh\u01b0 sau:\n\nBelow is the conversion table / D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng quy \u0111\u1ed5i:\n\n| 100 scores scale Thang \u0111i\u1ec3m 100 | Letter Grade \u0110i\u1ec3m b\u1eb1ng ch\u1eef | GPA score \u0110i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh t\u00ednh theo h\u1ec7 4 | Note Ghi ch\u00fa |\n| - | - | - | - |\n| 90-100 | A+ | 4 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 80-89 | A | 3.8 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 70-79 | A- | 3.6 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 65-69 | B+ | 3.4 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 60-64 | B | 3.2 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 55-59 | B- | 2.8 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 50-54 | C+ | 2.4 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 45-49 | C | 2.2 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 40-44 | C- | 2.0 | Pass / \u0110\u1ed7 |\n| 0-39 | F | 0 | Fail / Tr\u01b0\u1ee3t |\n\nAverage GPA is calculated as below: / \u0110i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh GPA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh theo c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c:\n\nAverage GPA = (GPA score module 1 x credit module 1 + GPA score module 2 x credit module 2 +\u2026.. + GPA score module n x credit module n) /Total credits\n\nGPA = (\u0110i\u1ec3m GPA m\u00f4n 1 x s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00edn ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc 1 + \u0111i\u1ec3m GPA m\u00f4n 2 x s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00edn ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc 2 + \u2026 + \u0111i\u1ec3m GPA m\u00f4n th\u1ee9 n x s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00edn ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc n)/ t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 t\u00edn ch\u1ec9", "metadata": {"file_name": "BUV-JUL24-FAQ.pdf", "page": "52-54"}, "type": "Document"}}